%80%99re%20told%20it%E2%80%99s%20near%20Madurai%5D%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20also%20been%20nursing%20her%20lifelong%20dream%20of%20owning%20a%20restaurant%20while%20being%20married%20to%20Prabhakar%20Shetty%20(Manoj%20Bajpayee).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabhakar%2C%20or%20as%20Swathi%20calls%20him%2C%20Prabhu%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20black%20sheep%20brother%20of%20the%20local%20mafia%20boss%2C%20Arvind%20Shetty%20(a%20wonderfully%20foul-mouthed%20Sayaji%20Shinde).%20In%20a%20brisk%20opening%20scene%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20established%20Prabhu%20and%20Swathi%20are%20passing%20each%20other%20on%20the%20downslope%20of%20their%20marriage%20of%20two%20decades.%20He%E2%80%99s%20stolen%20money%20from%20his%20brother%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2030%20crore%20for%20a%20business%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%20out.%20So%20he%E2%80%99s%20desperate%20to%20sell%20another%20scheme%20to%20him%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20invest%2C%20so%20he%20can%20find%20a%20way%20to%20bury%20his%20theft%20into%20the%20new%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20Swathi%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20revealed%20%E2%80%93%20is%20having%20an%20affair%20with%20Prabhu%E2%80%99s%20masseur%2C%20Umesh%20(also%20played%20by%20Bajpayee%2C%20with%20a%20squint%20in%20his%20left%20eye).%20Hopelessly%20in%20love%20with%20Swathi%2C%20Umesh%20looks%20a%20bit%20like%20Prabhu%2C%20but%20nobody%20really%20sees%20it%20except%20Arvind%2C%20and%20when%20the%20time%20comes%20%E2%80%93%20Swathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20air%20of%20strangeness%20pervades%20Abhishek%20Chaubey%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%20(co-created%20with%20Unaiza%20Merchant%2C%20Harshad%20Nalwade%2C%20and%20Anant%20Tripathi)%20%E2%80%93%20like%20a%20pulp%20novel%20adapted%20by%20the%20Coens.%20The%20dark%20comedy%20is%20fuelled%20by%20the%20clumsiness%20of%20first-time%20criminals%2C%20while%20some%20discover%20how%20proficient%20they%20can%20be%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20shot%20of%20the%20show%2C%20spanning%20eight%20episodes%20with%20a%20runtime%20of%20over%20seven%20hours%2C%20is%20scored%20with%20Offenbach%E2%80%99s%20Barcarolle%20%E2%80%93%20the%20symphony%20completely%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20rolling%20hills%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20falseness%20in%20the%20way%20the%20show%E2%80%99s%20characters%20refer%20to%20each%20other%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbabe%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cjaan%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20who%20probably%20grew%20up%20watching%20films%2C%20where%20they%20heard%20characters%20with%20similar%20social%20stature%20using%20such%20words.%20Like%20how%20the%20rich%20daughter%20of%20a%20certain%20vintage%20would%20waltz%20into%20a%20room%20screaming%20%E2%80%9CDaddy!%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20time%20when%20%E2%80%9CPitaji%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20way%20to%20refer%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20father.%20In%20%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20most%20of%20the%20primary%20characters%20seem%20to%20be%20performing%20while%20talking%20to%20each%20other.%20No%20one%20is%20particularly%20at%20peace%20with%20their%20place%20in%20the%20world%2C%20everyone%20wants%20more.%20Like%20most%20of%20us%2C%20even%20these%20beings%20are%20programmed%20to%20overreach.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20then%20that%20the%20soup%20hits%20the%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FGa0XeUKWTys%3Fsi%3Dofh_n6qiNUmbTZGO%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaubey%20and%20his%20co-creators%20write%20a%20busy%20show%2C%20where%20there%20are%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20narrative%20threads%20emerging%20from%20the%20central%20crime.%20Two%20characters%20die%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20episode%2C%20triggering%20a%20thick%20web%20of%20lies%2C%20deceit%2C%20and%20blackmail.%20It%E2%80%99s%20never%20really%20the%20mystery%20that%20is%20the%20selling%20point%20here%2C%20but%20the%20audience%20rooting%20for%20our%20two%20morally%20ambiguous%20anti-heroes%2C%20looking%20to%20get%20away%20with%20murder%2C%20and%20regretting%20it%20more%20than%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20both%20Prabhu%20and%20Umesh%2C%20Bajpayee%20showcases%20why%20he%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20most%20physical%20actors%20working%20today.%20After%20Devashish%20Makhija%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EJoram%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20where%20Bajpayee%E2%80%99s%20Dasru%20primarily%20depended%20on%20his%20body%20language%20to%20communicate%20%E2%80%93%20over%20here%20it%E2%80%99s%20his%20acid%20reflux%20(to%20avoid%20eating%20Swathi%E2%80%99s%20soup)%20that%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20beauty.%20As%20the%20reluctant%20Umesh%2C%20Bajpayee%20gives%20a%20sensational%20ode%20of%20Lady%20Macbeth%2C%20with%20guilt%20and%20petty%20jealousy%20getting%20the%20better%20of%20him%20on%20more%20than%20one%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaubey%20stacks%20the%20supporting%20cast%20with%20excellent%20names%20like%20Shinde%2C%20as%20the%20senior%20Shetty%20brother%2C%20incapable%20of%20saying%20a%20kind%20word%20to%20anyone%20alive.%20Nassar%20is%20hilarious%2C%20as%20the%20disillusioned%2C%20on-the-cusp-of-retirement%20cop%2C%20Hassan%2C%20who%20rediscovers%20his%20sense%20of%20duty%20after%20meeting%20a%20young%2C%20diligent%20cop%2C%20Thupalli%20(Anbuthasan)%2C%20eager%20to%20prove%20himself.%20Kani%20Kusruthi%2C%20is%20very%20good%20as%20the%20earnest%20accountant%20at%20Prabhu%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20funniest%2C%20most%20unexpected%20action%20scene%20in%20the%20show.%20Anula%20Navlekar%2C%20playing%20Apeksha%2C%20Arvind%20Shetty%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20%E2%80%93%20who%20wants%20to%20go%20to%20a%20Fine%20Arts%20school%20in%20Paris%2C%20to%20escape%20her%20controlling%20family%20%E2%80%94%20also%20gets%20more%20than%20one%20scene%20to%20shine.%20Like%20Swathi%2C%20she%20isn%E2%80%99t%20very%20good%20at%20Art%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20you%20can%20foot%20the%20bills%20of%20the%20world%2C%20you%20can%20continue%20to%20delude%20yourself%2C%20the%20show%20seems%20to%20imply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20masterstroke%20is%20the%20casting%20of%20Lal%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20mysterious%20Lucas%20%E2%80%93%20who%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20hinted%2C%20is%20a%20former%20member%20of%20rebel%20forces%2C%20trained%20in%20the%20jungles%2C%20capable%20of%20carrying%20out%20Shetty%E2%80%99s%20dirty%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20however%2C%20belongs%20to%20Sen%20Sharma%20%E2%80%93%20an%20actor%20who%20seems%20to%20have%20perfected%20the%20art%20of%20not%20doing%20too%20much.%20Like%20most%20great%20actors%20working%2C%20Sen%20Sharma%20is%20poised%20through%20most%20scenes%20when%20viewers%20might%20be%20screaming%20internally.%20It%E2%80%99s%20to%20Sen%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20credit%20that%20even%20though%20we%E2%80%99re%20appalled%20at%20Swathi%E2%80%99s%20actions%2C%20we%20never%20fail%20to%20see%20her%20desperation%20to%20rise%20above%20her%20mediocre%20life.%20The%20way%20her%20face%20contracts%20after%20being%20humiliated%20by%20her%20husband%20and%20his%20elder%20brother%2C%20to%20scenes%20where%20she%20looks%20out%20of%20her%20depth%20carrying%20out%20her%20rookie%20ransom%20plans%2C%20to%20scenes%20where%20she%E2%80%99s%20incredibly%20convincing%20as%20an%20evil%20mastermind%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20performance%20for%20the%20ages.%20Thereby%20solidifying%20the%20theory%20that%20Sen%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20OTT%20era%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20consistent%2C%20fertile%20bodies%20of%20work%20of%20all%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaubey%2C%20who%20has%20always%20leaned%20into%20genres%20to%20tell%20stories%20beyond%20them%2C%20is%20mostly%20content%20sticking%20to%20the%20genre%20mould%20here.%20Like%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fin-guns-gulaabs-raj-and-dk-are-in-good-form-but-you-can-see-the-gags-coming%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20which%20relied%20on%20easter%20eggs%20and%20pop-culture%20references%20%E2%80%93%20even%20Chaubey%20has%20his%20share%20of%20fun%20here.%20Prabhu%E2%80%99s%20resort%20company%20is%20called%20Last%20Resort%2C%20the%20resort%20he%20wishes%20to%20build%20is%20called%20Hotel%20California%2C%20also%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20ingenious%20needle%20drop%20of%20Nina%20Simone%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Sinnerman%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20which%20I%20last%20heard%20during%20a%20heist%20sequence%20in%20Pierce%20Brosnan-starrer%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Thomas%20Crown%20Affair%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1999).%20Even%20in%20%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewe%E2%80%99re%20witnessing%20a%20heist%2C%20only%20if%20new%20criminals%20could%20channel%20Brosnan%E2%80%99s%20reel%20composure.%20Instead%2C%20we%20get%20Sen%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20and%20Bajpayee%E2%80%99s%20asininity.%20As%20Chaubey%E2%80%99s%20show%20insists%2C%20this%20is%20real%20life%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704980116000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11182958%2Fimage-1720.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fkiller-soup-review-a-delicious-slow-cooked-broth-of-desperation-lies-and-foolishness%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20actor%20whatever%20the%20role%20shines%20in%20the%20film%2C%20Konkona%20Sen%20Sharma%20and%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%20most%20of%20all.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fkiller-soup-review-a-delicious-slow-cooked-broth-of-desperation-lies-and-foolishness%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Srinagar's%20Air%20Quality%3A%20How%20Vehicle%20Pollution%20and%20Power%20Shortages%20Have%20Been%20Worsening%20the%20Issue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11165359%2Fimage-1719.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOver%20the%20past%20month%2C%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20has%20consistently%20remained%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98poor%20category%E2%80%99%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20mornings%20and%20evenings%20when%20the%20temperature%20drops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20data%20from%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%2C%20the%20Ambient%20Air%20Quality%20Monitoring%20Centre%20at%20Rajbagh%2C%20Srinagar%2C%20recorded%20PM10%20levels%20as%20high%20as%20227.9%20and%20PM2.5%20levels%20of%2073.3%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20meter%20(%C2%B5g%2Fm3)%20on%20certain%20days%20in%20December.%20According%20to%20weather.com%2C%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20AQI%20was%20340%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20January%205%2C%20340%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20on%20January%206%2C%20311%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20on%20January%207%2C%20and%20321%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20on%20January%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20permissible%20limit%20of%20PM2.5%20levels%20in%20India%20is%2060%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20as%20per%20the%20revised%20guidelines%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20and%20Forestry.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20latest%20global%20air%20pollution%20standard%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fdata%2Fdata-which-major-indian-cities-exceed-whos-revised-pollution-limits%2Farticle36738211.ece%5C%22%3Eallows%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20an%20average%20of%20only%2015%20%CE%BCg%2Fm3%20of%20PM2.5%20concentration%20in%20a%2024-hour%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20available%20data%2C%20the%20carbon%20monoxide%20(CO)%20levels%20in%20the%20air%20reached%20as%20high%20as%20900%20%C2%B5g%2Fm3%20on%20most%20days%20during%20severe%20winter%20months.%20Other%20air%20quality-related%20websites%20also%20report%20similar%20findings.%20Both%20government%20and%20non-government%20sources%20indicate%20that%20air%20quality%20in%20Srinagar%20has%20been%20consistently%20concerning%20between%20November%20and%20February%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Winter%20Burst%20of%20Pristine%20Kashmir%20Valley%20Air%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-018-20601-z%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%202018%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Nature%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20revealed%20that%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20the%20PM2.5%20levels%20reached%20as%20high%20as%20348%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20during%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20study%20period.%20The%20permissible%20limit%20in%20India%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20is%2060%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Researchers%20attribute%20the%20poor%20air%20quality%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20human-related%20and%20natural%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20study%20revealed%20that%20calm%20winds%2C%20weak%20mixing%20conditions%2C%20temperature%20inversion%2C%20and%20a%20shallow%20planetary%20boundary%20layer%20are%20responsible%20for%20exacerbating%20the%20impact%20of%20widespread%20biomass%20fuel%20burning%20in%20winters%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20presence%20of%20transport%20exhaust%20and%20particulate%20matter%20carried%20from%20distant%20regions%20by%20westerlies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20%E2%80%98Particulate%20Pollution%20over%20an%20urban%20Himalayan%20site%3A%20Temporal%20variability%2C%20impact%20of%20meteorology%20and%20potential%20source%20regions%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F34371409%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Cem%3E%20Science%20of%20the%20Total%20Environment%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20authored%20by%20professor%20Shakil%20Romshoo%2C%20%3Cspan%3EMudasir%20Ahmad%20Bhat%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGufran%20Beig.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20delves%20deep%20into%20the%20status%20and%20causes%20of%20air%20pollution%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMass%20concentration%20of%20PM2.5%20and%20PM10%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20our%20study%20revealed%2C%20is%20higher%20than%20other%20high-altitude%20sites%20in%20Hindu%20Kush%20Himalayas%2C%E2%80%9D%20Romshoo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20poor%20air%20quality%20is%20a%20major%20concern%20for%20people%20with%20respiratory%20ailments.%20This%20has%20led%20medical%20professionals%20to%20call%20for%20stronger%20and%20consistent%20efforts%20to%20curtail%20controllable%20sources%20of%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20among%20the%20top%20four%20regions%20for%20chronic%20obstructive%20pulmonary%20disease%20(COPD)%2C%20with%20over%204%2C700%20people%20suffering%20from%20this%20respiratory%20disorder%20per%20lakh%20of%20the%20population.%20This%20number%20is%20twice%20as%20high%20as%20in%20most%20Indian%20states.%20COPD%20is%20also%20among%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanglo%2Farticle%2FPIIS2214-109X(18)30409-1%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3Etitled%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%98Burden%20of%20Chronic%20Respiratory%20Diseases%20and%20their%20heterogeneity%20across%20the%20states%20of%20India%3A%20the%20global%20burden%20of%20disease%20study%201990-2016%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Parvaiz%20A.%20Koul%2C%20pulmonologist%20and%20an%20avid%20researcher%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20contributing%20authors%20to%20this%20study.%20Currently%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20the%20director%20of%20Sher-i-Kashmir%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences.%20He%20said%20that%20every%20winter%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20hospitals%20face%20a%20deluge%20of%20patients%20with%20respiratory%20distress%20and%20ailments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20the%20highest%20prevalence%20of%20chronic%20airflow%20limitation%20in%20India%3A%20one%20in%20every%20five%20individuals%20over%20the%20age%20of%2040%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSmoking%20and%20air%20pollution%20are%20known%20contributing%20factors%2C%20although%20we%20need%20more%20research%20in%20these%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoul%20said%20that%20there%20may%20be%20a%20genetic%20factor%2C%20but%20genes%20could%20not%20be%20altered.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20need%20to%20work%20on%20external%20factors.%20%E2%80%9CDomestic%20and%20ambient%20air%20quality%20are%20the%20keys.%20Anything%20that%20pollutes%20the%20air%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20addressed%20on%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Road%20Transport%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20reveals%20that%20the%20vehicle%20population%20in%20Srinagar%20is%20approximately%204%20lakh%2C%20excluding%20vehicles%20from%20other%20districts%2C%20states%2C%20and%20those%20owned%20by%20the%20armed%20forces.%20The%20rate%20of%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20vehicles%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20has%20been%20unprecedented.%20Between%202012%20and%202017%2C%20there%20were%204%2C78%2C292%20new%20vehicle%20registrations%2C%20and%20this%20number%20surged%20to%207%2C84%2C503%20between%202017%20and%202022.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%2C%2024%25%20of%20households%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20own%20a%20car%2C%20the%20second-highest%20after%20Kerala.%20The%20dismal%20public%20transport%20situation%20necessitates%20the%20reliance%20on%20and%20usage%20of%20private%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20from%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Department%2C%20who%20requested%20anonymity%2C%20there%20is%20a%20shortage%20of%202%20lakh%20public%20transport%20seats%20per%20day%20in%20Srinagar.%20The%20emissions%20from%20the%20congested%20roads%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20ever-growing%20use%20of%20privately%20owned%20fossil%20fuel-burning%20vehicles%2C%20are%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20potential%20health%20and%20environmental%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20on%20particulate%20pollution%20by%20Romshoo%20advocates%20a%20strict%20check%20on%20emissions%20from%20coal%20burning%2C%20dusty%20roads%2C%20wood%20burning%2C%20and%20vehicular%20traffic.%20It%20calls%20for%20the%20utilisation%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20hydroelectric%20potential%20to%20replace%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20wood%20burning%20in%20winters.%20However%2C%20Kashmir%20faces%20acute%20power%20shortages%20that%20get%20worse%20in%20winters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Naveed%20Nazir%20Shah%2C%20head%20of%20the%20pulmonology%20department%20at%20the%20Chest%20Diseases%20Hospital%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20said%20that%20power%20shortages%20force%20people%20to%20use%20wood%20and%20coal-based%20heating%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20contributing%20to%20indoor%20air%20pollution.%20Furthermore%2C%20individuals%20relying%20on%20oxygen%20therapy%20face%20challenges%20as%20they%20do%20not%20receive%20round-the-clock%20electricity%20to%20operate%20the%20essential%20oxygen%20concentrators%20they%20depend%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20patient%20number%20has%20been%20increasing%20threefold%20every%20winter.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20infections%2C%20the%20allergies%2C%20the%20COPD%2C%20everything%20worsens%20with%20cold%20and%20the%20smog%20that%20we%20have%20in%20Srinagar.%20The%20power%20shortages%20are%20also%20affecting%20us%20in%20many%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704980044000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt