hould%20be%20using%20AI%20to%20holistically%20connect%20with%20their%20customers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStagwell's%20new%20AI%20tool%2C%20SmartAssets%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbc4i.com%2Fbusiness%2Fpress-releases%2Fcision%2F20240103NY03509%2Fstagwell-stgw-to-debut-smartassets-at-ces-2024-as-it-rolls-out-client-solutions-around-three-es-of-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erolled%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20CES%202024%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20is%20designed%20to%20analyze%20individual%20parts%20of%20ad%20creative%20and%20performance%20data%20and%20iterate%20future%20campaigns.%20It%20was%20developed%20by%20Locaria%2C%20a%20digital%20language%20agency%20in%20the%20Stagwell%20Group%2C%20which%20won%20an%20internal%20competition%20to%20create%20the%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20to%20Stagwell%20CEO%2C%20Mark%20Penn%2C%20in%20December%20about%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%2C%20its%20applications%20at%20Stagwell%2C%20and%20why%20b-to-c%20companies%20need%20to%20focus%20use%20AI%20to%20connect%20with%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20Q%26amp%3BA%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20AI%20compare%20to%20other%20digital%20innovation%20trends%20that%20have%20surfaced%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20metaverse%20or%20some%20other%20trends%2C%20the%20power%20of%20AI%2C%20what%20it%20can%20do%2C%20and%20what%20companies%20need%20to%20do%20to%20harness%20it%20is%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20big%20change%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20way%20that%20people%20can%20communicate%20with%20computers.%20You%20can%20ask%20a%20computer%20to%20do%20something%2C%20and%20the%20its%20ability%20to%20understand%20you%20and%20then%20do%20it%20is%20a%20quantum%20leap%20from%20the%20clipped%20phrases%20that%20we%20stick%20into%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20does%20SmartAsset%20do%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20SmartAsset%20product%20takes%20a%20piece%20of%20content%20and%2C%20as%20I%20like%20to%20say%2C%20puts%20it%20through%20a%20car%20wash.%20It%20breaks%20it%20down%20and%20sees%20that%20there's%20%5Bfor%20example%5D%20a%20cat%2C%20a%20dog%2C%20a%20baby.%20It%20understands%20those%20elements%20and%20gets%20test%20results%20on%20how%20the%20content%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20danger%20is%20if%20clients%20don't%20use%20what%20we%20call%20%26quot%3Bprivate%20ChatGPT%26quot%3B%20then%20they%20will%20be%20giving%20out%20their%20information%20and%20data%20into%20the%20larger%20pool.%20We're%20giving%20clients%20a%20kind%20of%20moat%20around%20which%20AI%20can%20be%20utilized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20build%20private%20spaces%20that%20utilize%20their%20data%20to%20give%20them%20unique%20understanding%20and%20results%2C%20otherwise%20they'll%20just%20get%20the%20same%20thing%20that%20everybody%20else%20gets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20are%20you%20using%20AI%20at%20Stagwell%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInternally%20we%20were%20looking%20at%20processes%20that%20can%20be%20sped%20up%20or%20made%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20working%20on%20surveys%2C%20I%20needed%20about%2063%20people%20to%20do%20a%20survey.%20Now%20we%20can%20do%20the%20same%20project%20with%20two%20or%20three%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20creating%20efficient%20products%20for%20use%20in%20communications%2C%20research%2C%20and%20media.%20PRofet%20is%20one%20%E2%80%94%20it%20uses%20generative%20AI%20to%20help%20people%20create%20a%20news%20release%2C%20figure%20out%20who's%20going%20to%20cover%20it%20favorably%2C%20and%20then%20write%20the%20pitches.%20It's%20a%20very%20useful%20product.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20also%20have%20research%20products%20that%20help%20people%20do%20their%20own%20surveys%20and%20use%20AI%20to%20analyze%20focus%20groups%20and%20find%20statistically%20relevant%20findings%20and%20articulate%20them.%20The%20research%20community%20laps%20up%20technology%20very%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20will%20make%20image%20creation%2C%20testing%2C%20and%20analysis%20fundamentally%20more%20efficient%2C%20in%20the%20same%20ways%20that%20I%20saw%20my%20survey%20business%20become%20more%20efficient%20every%20three%20or%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20do%20you%20foster%20innovation%20and%20adoption%20of%20new%20technologies%20internally%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20created%20the%20Stagwell%20Marketing%20Cloud%20group%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20differentiating%20elements%20here%20was%20to%20have%20innovation%20at%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20private%20AI%20environment%20internally.%20So%20right%20now%20all%20of%20our%20agencies%20come%20forward%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20could%20use%20AI%20for%20X%26quot%3B.%20We%20take%20their%20idea%2C%20and%20we%20decide%20which%20ones%20we're%20going%20to%20program%20or%20engineer%20for%20them.%20About%20250%20people%20internally%20are%20signed%20up%20against%20our%20central%2C%20internal%20AI%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20process%20for%20helping%20each%20of%20the%20agencies%20come%20up%20with%20ideas%20and%20manage%20the%20deployment.%20At%20some%20of%20the%20%5Badvertising%5D%20holding%20companies%2C%20everyone%20sort%20of%20does%20their%20own%20thing%20in%20the%20corner.%20We%20really%20try%20to%20get%20everybody%20on%20the%20central%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDo%20you%20think%20the%20marketing%20sector%20is%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20AI%20ultimately%20doing%20the%20jobs%20currently%20done%20by%20humans%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20in%20the%20pure%20advertising%20space%20there's%20anxiety%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20look%20at%20advertising%20itself%20and%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20really%20generate%20tier-one%20%5Bpremium%5D%20content%2C%20I%20always%20say%20AI%20is%20having%20an%20entire%20group%20of%20C%20students.%20You%20can%20get%20a%20lot%20done%20with%20C%20students%2C%20but%20there's%20still%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20stuff%20you'll%20never%20get%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20think%20that%20the%20tier-one%20content%20could%20be%20facilitated%2C%20%3Cbr%3Ewith%20some%20assistance%20to%20make%20it%20easier.%20Just%20as%20processing%20data%20became%20so%20much%20easier%20for%20surveys%20when%20I%20was%20doing%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20tier-two%20%5Bstock%5D%20content%20has%20a%20lot%20more%20danger%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20ability%20to%20have%20somebody%20create%20it.%20There%20is%20going%20to%20be%20real%20dislocation%20over%20time%20in%20that%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20do%20you%20counsel%20clients%20that%20want%20to%20get%20started%20in%20AI%2C%20but%20are%20intimidated%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPick%20off%20bite-sized%20projects%20you%20can%20do%20as%20a%20demonstration.%20Take%20your%20last%20year%20of%20focus%20groups%2C%20run%20it%20through%20AI%2C%20and%20see%20the%20analysis%20and%20recommendations%20produced%20through%20that%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20about%20taking%20a%20need%20and%20narrowing%20it%20down%20to%20something%20practical%2C%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20boil%20the%20ocean.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20biggest%20thing%20consumer%20companies%20should%20look%20at%20is%20how%20to%20change%20the%20interaction%20between%20your%20company%20and%20the%20consumer%2C%20through%20a%20natural%20language%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESay%20you're%20an%20office%20supply%20company.%20On%20its%20website%2C%20you%20could%20just%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20have%20an%20office%20party.%26quot%3B%20The%20website%20will%20ask%2C%20how%20many%20people%20you're%20having%2C%20what%20time%2C%20any%20holidays%3F%20And%20then%20from%20that%20it'll%20tell%20you%20all%20of%20the%20things%20you%20need%20to%20buy%2C%20and%20which%20are%20the%20top%20rated%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20kind%20of%20interaction%20where%20it%20greatly%20simplifies%20the%20tasks%20that%20you're%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20will%20your%20company%20interact%20more%20