t%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20nap%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20otherwise%20return%20to%20their%20home%2C%20dormitory%2C%20or%20homeroom%20to%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20also%20perform%20eye%20exercises%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20intended%20to%20alleviate%20stress%20and%20eye%20tension%20throughout%20long%20hours%20of%20study%20%E2%80%94%20and%20student%20monitors%20will%20check%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20classmates%20are%20participating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20students%20have%20so%20many%20extracurricular%20activities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20ask%20my%20students%20about%20their%20plans%20for%20the%20evening%20or%20weekend%2C%20they%20respond%20with%20a%20list%20of%20extracurricular%20activities%3A%20badminton%2C%20calligraphy%2C%20French%20or%20Spanish%20courses%2C%20soccer%20club%2C%20choir%2C%20violin%2C%20piano%2C%20or%20a%20science%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20rigorous%20and%20multifaceted%20education%20is%20a%20priority%20and%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20means%20of%20economic%20mobility%20as%20well%20as%20status.%20China%20boasts%20a%20nearly%20flawless%20high%20school%20graduation%20rate%2C%20and%20students%20often%20begin%20their%20education%20in%20an%20early%20years%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20students%20are%20mostly%20first-language%20Mandarin%20speakers%2C%20throughout%20primary%20school%2C%20many%20quickly%20attain%20reading%20levels%20in%20English%20equivalent%20to%20their%20American%20counterparts.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Math%20materials%20I%20use%20in%20planning%20for%20my%20first-grade%20students%20are%20often%20US%20second%20or%20third-grade%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EViolence%20in%20school%20campuses%20is%20really%20low%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20each%20school%20will%20have%20at%20least%20one%20security%20guard%2C%20their%20concern%20is%20not%20policing%20the%20students%20but%20protecting%20them%20from%20outsiders.%20Violence%20on%20school%20campuses%20in%20China%20is%20infrequent%20enough%20that%20most%20students%20and%20teachers%20simpl