arfare%2C%20per%20the%C2%A0Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20comes%20as%20China%20looks%20to%20expand%20its%20military%20reach%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20mapping%20vast%20areas%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20civilian%20research%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20could%20be%20to%20plan%20submarine%20warfare%2C%20a%20think%20tank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20new%20study%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffeatures.csis.org%2Fhiddenreach%2Fchina-indian-ocean-research-vessels%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenter%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20(CSIS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20think%20tank%20said%20that%20Chinese%20vessels%20carrying%20out%20civilian%20oceanographic%20research%20projects%20were%20also%20likely%20collecting%20data%20for%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20to%20help%20plan%20potential%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CSIS%20said%20that%20while%20much%20of%20the%20research%20was%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-destroyer-challenges-chinese-claims-in-south-china-sea-2022-1%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20western%20Pacific%20and%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Chinese%20research%20vessels%20were%20increasingly%20focusing%20on%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20Chinese%20surveys%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20contribute%20to%20scientific%20and%20commercial%20efforts%2C%20the%20data%20collected%20on%20research%20missions%20has%20clear%20military%20value%E2%80%94especially%20to%20submarine%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20these%20require%20reliable%20information%20on%20complicated%20undersea%20conditions%20to%20ensure%20their%20safety%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20data%20from%20Windward%2C%20a%20maritime%20AI%20data%20company%2C%20the%20think%20tank%20said%20it%20found%20that%20Chinese%20research%20boats%20had%20conducted%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20hours%20of%20operations%20globally%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20found%20that%20many%20of%20these%20vessels%20displayed%20suspicious%20behavior%2C%20such%20as%20docking%20at%20ports%20with%20Chinese%20%26quot%3Bmilitary-affiliated%20facilities%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20could%20be%20linked%20to%20Beijing%20and%20its%20geopolitical%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20many%20of%20these%20vessels%20went%20%26quot%3Bdark%26quot%3B%20or%20turned%20off%20identification%20systems%20when%20in%20sensitive%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20undersea%20mapping%20appears%20to%20be%20part%20of%20China's%20military-civil%20fusion%20strategy%2C%20where%20civilian%20companies%20or%20research%20can%20be%20co-opted%20for%20military%20purposes%2C%20the%20CSIS%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Ocean%20is%20a%20vital%20area%20for%20China's%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20and%20economic%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Funaiole%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20CSIS%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20report%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2024%2F01%2F10%2Fchina-submarine-military-indian-ocean%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BBeijing%20is%20serious%20about%20fielding%20a%20blue-water%20navy%2C%20one%20that%20will%20be%20active%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20and%20blurring%20the%20lines%20between%20its%20research%20ecosystem%20and%20its%20national%20security%20apparatus%20will%20help%20it%20get%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20amid%20China's%20souring%20relationship%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Scobell%2C%20a%20distinguished%20fellow%20with%20the%20China%20program%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usip.org%2Fpublications%2F2023%2F10%2Fthree-things-know-about-china-india-tensions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%20Institute%20of%20Peace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20in%20October%20that%20China%20considered%20India%20as%20intent%20on%20%26quot%3Bcollaborating%20with%20other%20powers%20to%20contain%20China's%20rise%20and%20counter%20China's%20growing%20presence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20added%20that%20China%20would%20likely%20try%20to%20retain%20%26quot%3Bcordial%26quot%3B%20ties%20with%20India%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%20as%20it%20wanted%20%26quot%3Bto%20keep%20New%20Delhi%20contained%20in%20a%20geostrategic%20South%20Asian%20box%20with%20the%20lid%20on%20tight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20India's%20part%2C%20it%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20the%20research%20vessels'%20activities%2C%20and%20it%20has%20pressured%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20temporarily%20ban%20foreign%20research%20boats%20from%20its%20ports%20over%20concerns%20that%20Chinese%20vessels%20are%20being%20used%20for%20covert%20military%20purposes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsri-lanka-india-china-research-ships-42ddb725105eb32b3b43fee8fff3838c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-produces-vast-undersea-maps-submarine-warfare-report-says-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704978062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659fc2726979d7371822553f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-produces-vast-undersea-maps-submarine-warfare-report-says-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%20research%20vessels%20have%20conducted%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20hours%20of%20operations%20globally%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-produces-vast-undersea-maps-submarine-warfare-report-says-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Afcon%202023%3A%20Gambia%20coach%20feared%20team%20would%20die%20on%20aborted%20flight%20to%20Ivory%20Coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704978037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_sport%2F11983%2Fproduction%2F_132276027_whatsappimage2024-01-11at09.04.42.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Fafrica%2F67944871%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gambia%20squad%20travelling%20to%20the%20Africa%20Cup%20of%20Nations%20%26quot%3Bcould%20have%20died%26quot%3B%20on%20an%20aborted%20flight%2C%20claims%20coach%20Tom%20Saintfiet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A817%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Fafrica%2F67944871%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Fafrica%2F67944871.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Fafrica%2F67944871.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Knife%2C%20Towel%2C%20Pillow%3A%20Clues%20CEO%20Accused%20Of%20Killing%20Son%20Left%20Behind%20In%20Goa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20knife%2C%20towel%20and%20pillow%20-%20these%20seemingly%20simple%20items%20could%20help%20the%20police%20solve%20an%20intriguing%20murder%20case%20where%20a%20mother%20-%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20Bengaluru%20startup%20-%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20killing%20her%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20recovered%20the%20three%20items%20from%20the%20service%20apartment%20she%20had%20stayed%20at%20in%20Goa.%20Ms%20Seth%20checked%20into%20the%20apartment%20in%20Candolim%20on%20January%206%20and%20stayed%20there%20till%20January%208.%20She%20allegedly%20killed%20her%20son%20in%20the%20apartment%20and%20stuffed%20the%20body%20in%20a%20bag%20before%20taking%20it%20to%20neighbouring%20Karnataka%20in%20a%20taxi%20on%20Monday%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20apartment%20staff%20went%20to%20clean%20the%20room%2C%20they%20found%20blood%20stains%20on%20a%20towel.%20The%20staff%20immediately%20informed%20the%20police%20and%20told%20them%20that%20she%20carried%20an%20unusually%20heavy%20bag%2C%20and%20her%20son%20was%20not%20seen%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-year-old%20child%20was%20smothered%20to%20death%20either%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth%20or%20a%20pillow%2C%20the%20post-mortem%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20may%20have%20tried%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%20by%20slashing%20her%20wrist%20and%20later%20used%20the%20towel%20to%20stop%20the%20bleeding%2C%20the%20police%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recovery%20list%20from%20the%20crime%20scene%20includes%20a%20knife%2C%20a%20distinctive%20red%20bag%2C%20a%20towel%2C%20and%20a%20pillow%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20police%20officials%20called%20up%20Ms%20Seth%2C%20who%20was%20then%20in%20the%20cab%20in%20Bengaluru%20Bengaluru%20-%20to%20explain%20the%20blood%20stains%2C%20she%20said%20they%20were%20due%20to%20her%20monthly%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20them%20that%20he%20was%20at%20a%20friend's%20place%20and%20even%20gave%20the%20officials%20a%20fake%20address.%20The%20officials%20then%20spoke%20to%20the%20cab%20driver%20in%20Konkani%20to%20avoid%20suspicion%20by%20Ms%20Seth%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20take%20the%20vehicle%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20the%2039-year-old%20was%20caught%20with%20the%20red%20bag%20that%20she%20used%20to%20carry%20his%20son's%20body.%20She%20was%20arrested%20from%20Chitradurga%20in%20Karnataka%20on%20Monday%20night%20and%20brought%20to%20Goa%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20who%20are%20yet%20to%20find%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20murder%20took%20Ms%20Seth%20for%20a%20routine%20checkup%20today.%20She%20was%20also%20given%20a%20psychological%20examination%2C%20police%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Seth%20shows%20%26quot%3Bno%20remorse%26quot%3B%20over%20her%20son's%20death%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20last%20night.%20In%20fact%2C%20sources%20said%20Ms%20Seth%2C%20in%20police%20custody%20till%20next%20week%2C%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bnon-cooperative%26quot%3B%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20has%20denied%20her%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime%20during%20the%20interrogation%20and%20claimed%20the%20child%20was%20already%20dead%20when%20she%20got%20up%20from%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20are%20examining%20Suchana%20Seth's%20Call%20Detail%20Records%20(CDR)%20to%20unravel%20her%20contacts%20and%20conversations%20in%20the%20three%20days%20surrounding%20the%20incident%2C%20aiming%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20any%20potential%20collaborators%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20taxi%20she%20travelled%20by%20is%20still%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Seth%20has%20also%20told%20interrogators%20about%20her%20troubled%20marriage%20and%20as%20per%20sources%2C%20she%20allegedly%20killed%20her%20son%20reportedly%20over%20a%20custody%20battle%20with%20her%20estranged%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20couple's%20divorce%20documents%2C%20Ms%20Seth%20had%20filed%20a%20domestic%20violence%20case%20in%20August%202022%20against%20her%20estranged%20husband%20Venkat%20Raman.%20She%20had%20accused%20him%20of%20physically%20abusing%20her%20and%20her%20son%2C%20a%20charge%20Venkat%20Raman%20has%20denied%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenkat%20Raman%20reached%20Hiriyur%20in%20Chitradurga%20district%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20and%20took%20possession%20of%20his%20son's%20body%20after%20the%20post-mortem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Goa%20police%20would%20take%20Suchana%20Seth%20to%20the%20service%20ap