d%20Netflix%20India's%20content%20head.%20The%20First%20Information%20Report%2C%20filed%20by%20a%20right-wing%20outfit%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Jabalpur%2C%20alleges%20that%20the%20accused%20hurt%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20Hindus%2C%20disrespected%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20promoted%20'love%20jihad'%20through%20the%20movie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20at%20the%20Omti%20police%20station%20by%20fringe%20outfit%20Hindu%20Sewa%20Parishad%20and%20names%20seven%20accused%2C%20including%20Nayanthara%2C%20director%20Nilesh%20Krishnaa%2C%20producers%20Jatin%20Sethi%20and%20R%20Ravindran%2C%20and%20Netflix%20India's%20content%20head%20Monika%20Shergill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%2C%20which%20released%20in%20theatres%20on%20December%201%2C%20began%20streaming%20on%20Netflix%20on%20December%2029.%20After%20a%20backlash%20and%20several%20police%20complaints%2C%20it%20has%20now%20been%20pulled%20from%20the%20OTT%20platform.%20Two%20complaints%20against%20Nayanthara%20and%20others%20have%20also%20been%20filed%20in%20Mumbai%20by%20right-wing%20outfits%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20Hindu%20IT%20Cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jabalpur%20case%2C%20by%20Hindu%20Sewa%20Parishad's%20founder%20and%20president%20Atul%20Jeswani%2C%20has%20been%20filed%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20sections%20pertaining%20to%20promoting%20enmity%20among%20groups%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20and%20common%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Sewa%20Parishad%20has%20alleged%20that%20%3Cem%3E'Annapoorani'%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20hurt%20Hindu%20religious%20sentiments%2C%20insulted%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20and%20made%20baseless%20comments%20against%20Lord%20Ram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20points%20to%20certain%20scenes%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20including%20one%20where%20Nayanthara%2C%20who%20plays%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20temple%20priest%2C%20offers%20%3Cem%3Enamaz%3C%2Fem%3E%20wearing%20a%20hijab%20before%20making%20biryani.%20It%20also%20claims%20that%2C%20in%20one%20segment%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20the%20character%20played%20by%20Nayanthara%20%26quot%3Bbrainwashes%26quot%3B%20her%20into%20cutting%20meat%2C%20%26quot%3Bclaiming%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Goddess%20Sita%20also%20consumed%20meat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jeswani%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20movie%20promotes%20'love%20jihad'%2C%20which%20is%20a%20term%20used%20by%20some%20right-wing%20outfits%20to%20allege%20attempted%20conversion%20of%20Hindu%20girls%20and%20women%20by%20Muslim%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELens%20On%20Timing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20just%20days%20away%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20complainants%20have%20also%20pointed%20to%20this.%20Many%20on%20social%20media%20have%20agreed%20with%20the%20complainants'%20allegations%20and%20called%20for%20action%20against%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20political%20controversy%20has%20also%20broken%20out%20over%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20brass%20stating%20that%20it%20will%20not%20attend%20the%20event%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20BJP%20has%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20party%20and%20several%20other%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-poster-targets-opposition-for-rejecting-ram-temple-event-invite-4842667%5C%22%3Ereleased%20a%20poster%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleging%20that%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20is%20anti-Sanatana%20Dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704977580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fvmfg4fg_nayanthara_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffir-against-actor-nayanthara-for-alleged-disrespect-to-lord-ram-in-tamil-movie-annapoorani-4842234%22%2C%22su