ceremony%20shows%20that%20the%20party%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9CGandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20Congress%2C%20this%20is%20not%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress.%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20political%20view%20was%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20he%20used%20to%20sing%20%E2%80%98Raghupati%20Raghav%20Raja%20Ram%E2%80%99%2C%20his%20samadhi%20(cremation%20spot)%20%E2%80%98Hey%20Ram%E2%80%99%20is%20written.%20Today%20that%20Ram%20Rajya%20is%20being%20started%20with%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20and%20Congress%20is%20not%20attending.%20This%20makes%20it%20very%20clear%20the%20difference%20between%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20and%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Trivedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20said%20that%20its%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20his%20predecessor%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20%E2%80%93%20who%20received%20the%20invitation%2C%20declined%20the%20invitation%20calling%20it%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbreaking-congress-declines-invitation-to-ram-temple-inauguration-calls-its-clearly-an-rss-bjp-event%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CRSS%2FBJP%20event%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congress-clearly-saying-january-22-is-part-of-rss-bjps-political-project-matters%5C%22%3EWhy%20Congress%20Clearly%20Saying%20January%2022%20Is%20Part%20of%20RSS%2FBJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Political%20Project%E2%80%99%20Matters%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReligion%20is%20a%20personal%20matter.%20But%20the%20RSS%2FBJP%20have%20long%20made%20a%20political%20project%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20inauguration%20of%20the%20incomplete%20temple%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20has%20be