l%20AMOLED%20displays%20are%20the%20same%20on%20the%20Fold%205%20and%20Fold%204.%20Regarding%20image%20quality%20and%20refresh%20rate%20(still%20a%20silky%20120Hz)%2C%20we%20can't%20really%20complain%2C%20as%20both%20are%20excellent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fold%205%20does%20pull%20ahead%20in%20one%20aspect%2C%20though%2C%20as%20it's%20a%20bit%20brighter%20than%20the%20Fold%204%2C%20coming%20in%20at%201750%20nits%2C%20a%20nice%20bump%20up%20from%20the%201200%20nits%20of%20the%20Fold%204.%20Those%20numbers%20can%20be%20a%20little%20misleading%2C%20though%2C%20as%20the%20jump%20up%20isn't%20as%20big%20as%20those%20numbers%20suggest%20when%20you%20put%20the%20two%20phones%20side-by-side.%20It's%20noticeable%2C%20sure%2C%20but%20not%20by%20much.%20Direct%20sunlight%20or%20aggressive%20fluorescent%20tube%20lighting%20can%20still%20make%20things%20difficult%2C%20especially%20with%20light%20sometimes%20reflecting%20more%20off%20the%20display%20crease%20in%20such%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20looking%20at%20white%20images%2C%20like%20most%20website%20backgrounds%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20slight%20yellow%20tinge%20to%20the%20Fold%205%2C%20and%20some%20colors%20appear%20a%20touch%20muted%20on%20the%20newer%20phone%2C%20too.%20Not%20in%20a%20bad%20way%2C%20though%2C%20as%20the%20contrast%20between%20shades%20is%20a%20touch%20more%20refined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20talk%20about%20the%20crease.%20Despite%20a%20redesigned%20and%20flatter%20hinge%2C%20the%20crease%20has%20no%20visible%20reduction.%20It's%20not%20particularly%20visible%20when%20viewed%20head-on%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20though%2C%20and%20it%20really%20doesn't%20bother%20me%20that%20much.%20What%20bothers%20me%20is%20how%20Samsung%20isn't%20%3Cem%3Etrying%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20flatten%20it%20out%20over%20the%20last%20three%20phones%20now%20when%20various%20Chinese%20foldables%20are%20getting%20very%20close%20to%20eradicating%20the%20crease%2C%20even%20if%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20coming%20at%20the%20cost%20of