ot%20contact%20the%20couple%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%20quoting%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coroner's%20office%20is%20carrying%20out%20an%20autopsy%20to%20determine%20the%20exact%20cause%20of%20the%20couple's%20death.%20No%20foul%20play%20is%20suspected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirefighters%20also%20checked%20the%20carbon%20dioxide%20levels%20in%20the%20home%20and%20did%20not%20find%20that%20they%20were%20above%20normal%2C%20said%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704973440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F6835sp0g_us-police-generic_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felderly-us-couple-found-dead-at-home-with-heater-at-537-degree-celsius-4842655%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20paramedics%20who%20attempted%20to%20take%20their%20body%20temperatures%20found%20that%20it%20topped%20the%20measurable%20index%20-%20well%20above%2098.6%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20the%20standard%20body%20temperature%20of%20most%20adults.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felderly-us-couple-found-dead-at-home-with-heater-at-537-degree-celsius-4842655%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felderly-us-couple-found-dead-at-home-with-heater-at-537-degree-celsius-4842655%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felderly-us-couple-found-dead-at-home-with-heater-at-537-degree-celsius-4842655%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airbnb%2C%20U'khand%20Tourism%20sign%20initial%20pact%20to%20enhance%20hospitality%20standards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704973401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-05%2F14%2Ffull%2F1620986095-8338.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompan