nt%20videos%20and%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20posturing%20isn't%20necessarily%20overstated.%20Last%20year's%20China%20Military%20Power%20Report%20from%20the%20Pentagon%20sounded%20the%20alarms%20on%20PLARF's%20bolstered%20missile%20capabilities%2C%20with%20some%20stockpiles%20doubling%20or%20nearly%20doubling%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DF-26s%2C%20intermediate-range%20ballistic%20missiles%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BGuam%20Killers%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20potential%20to%20hit%20American%20forces%20on%20the%20island%2C%20went%20from%20300%20in%202021%20to%20500%20during%20the%20following%20year.%20These%20weapons%20are%20also%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-growing-df-26-missile-arsenal-more-than-carrier-killers-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bcarrier%20killers%26quot%3B%20given%20their%20anti-ship%20role%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Military%20vehicles%20carrying%20DF-26%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20drive%20past%20the%20Tiananmen%20Gate%20during%20a%20military%20parade%20to%20mark%20the%2070th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20end%20of%20World%20War%20Two%20on%20September%203%2C%202015%2C%20in%20Beijing%2C%20China.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6536bc020487ff031cabf498%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMilitary%20vehicles%20carrying%20DF-26%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20drive%20past%20the%20Tiananmen%20Gate%20during%20a%20military%20parade%20to%20mark%20the%2070th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20end%20of%20World%20War%20Two%20on%20September%203%2C%202015%2C%20in%20Beijing%2C%20China.%3Cp%3EAndy%20Wong%20-%20Pool%20%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20significant%20increase%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20stockpile%20of%20DF-26s%20is%20concerning%20considering%20they%2C%20like%20the%20Chinese%20military's%20medium-range%20DF-21%2