r%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20'National%20Icon'%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20has%20voluntarily%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcknowledging%20his%20role%20as%20a%20political%20leader%20in%20an%20upcoming%20film%2C%20actor%20%40PankajTripathi%20has%20voluntarily%20stepped%20down%20as%20%23ECI%20National%20Icon%20as%20per%20terms%20of%20MoU.%20%23ECI%20expresses%20gratitude%20for%20his%20impactful%20contribution%20to%20voter%20awareness%20%26amp%3B%20%23SVEEP%20since%20Oct%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20social%20media%20handle%20of%20ECI%2C%20posted%20by%20Spokesperson%20ECI%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAcknowledging%20his%20role%20as%20a%20political%20leader%20in%20an%20upcoming%20film%2C%20actor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpankajtripathi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PankajTripathi%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20voluntarily%20stepped%20down%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FECI%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ECI%3C%2Fa%3E%20National%20Icon%20as%20per%20terms%20of%20MoU.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FECI%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ECI%3C%2Fa%3E%20expresses%20gratitude%20for%20his%20impactful%20contribution%20to%20voter%20awareness%20%26amp%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSVEEP%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SVEEP%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20Oct%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F83Ols8B9TY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F83Ols8B9TY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Spokesperson%20ECI%20(%40SpokespersonECI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpokespersonECI%2Fstatus%2F1745358017380454432%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EPankaj%20Tripathi%20was%20roped%20in%20as%20the%20ECI%20National%20Icon%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20days%20he%20is%20occupied%20promoting%20his%20upcoming%20project%20'Main%20Atal%20Hoon'.%20Recently%2C%20he%20talked%20about%20his%20interest%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tripathi%20is%20playing%20the%20role%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20in%20the%20biopic%20'Main%20Atal%20Hoon'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20Mr%20Tripathi%20spoke%20about%20his%20interest%20in%20becoming%20a%20politician%20in%20his%20home%20state%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20a%20politician%20in%20Bihar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tripathi%2C%20who%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%20during%20his%20college%20days%20in%20Bihar%2C%20said%20he%20had%20never%20thought%20about%20joining%20politics%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20thought%20about%20entering%20politics%20at%20that%20time.%20There%20was%20a%20thought%20that%20I%20might%20proceed%20in%20this%20line%20but%20then%20there%20was%20an%20arrest%20and%20the%20cops%20beat%20me%20up%20so%20I%20left%20that%20thought%20there%20and%20then.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20became%20inclined%20towards%20plays%20and%20dramas%20and%20after%20watching%20those%2C%20I%20got%20more%20attracted%20towards%20theatre.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20during%20the%20trailer%20launch%20of%20his%20soon-to-be%20released%20biopic%20on%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20he%20had%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20interest%20in%20politics%20and%20how%20he%20prepared%20for%20his%20role%20portraying%20the%20late%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recalled%20a%20funny%20anecdote%20from%20his%20college%20days%20when%20he%20joined%20the%20ABVP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20a%20youth%20wing.%20I%20have%20participated%20in%20andolans.%20I%20was%20even%20jailed%20for%20a%20week!%20Toh%20main%20uss%20raaste%20pe%20nikal%20chuka%20tha.%20Then%20I%20realised%20that%20the%20path%20of%20politics%20is%20full%20of%20thorns.%20Hence%2C%20I%20took%20a%20turn%20and%20started%20developing%20an%20interest%20in%20street%20theatre.%20There%20was%20Kaildas%20Rangalaya%2C%20Patna%20where%20I%20enrolled%20myself.%20Mujhe%20laga%20ki%20yeh%20behtar%20hai.%20Yahaan%20kam%20se%20kam%20bol%20ke%20acting%20hoti%20hai%20ki%20'main%20acting%20kar%20raha%20hoon'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tripathi%20quipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20'Main%20Atal%20Hoon'%20is%20directed%20by%20Ravi%20Jadhav%20and%20will%20be%20released%20on%20January%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20that%20he%20is%20honoured%20to%20bring%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20story%20to%20silver%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20the%20film%2C%20the%20journey%20of%20playing%20Shri%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20is%20really%20close%20to%20my%20heart.%20The%20man%20is%20truly%20a%20legend%2C%20and%20we%20are%20honoured%20to%20bring%20his%20inspiring%20story%20to%20the%20world.%20I%20hope%20audiences%20appreciate%20our%20efforts%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20legacy%20of%20Atal%20ji%20onto%20the%20big%20screens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20backed%20by%20Bhanushali%20Studios%20Limited%20and%20Legend%20Studios%2C%20Vinod%20Bhanushali%2C%20Sandeep%20Singh%2C%20Sam%20Khan%20and%20Kamlesh%20Bhanushali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704971880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fckp23v0g_pankaj-tripathi_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-pankaj-tripathi-steps-down-as-election-commissions-national-icon-4842458%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Pankaj%20Tripathi%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20'National%20Icon'%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20has%20voluntarily%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20position.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-pankaj-tripathi-steps-down-as-election-commissions-national-icon-4842458%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-pankaj-tripathi-steps-down-as-election-commissions-national-icon-4842458%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-pankaj-tripathi-steps-down-as-election-commissions-national-icon-4842458%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Issues%20Contempt%20Notices%20to%20Gujarat%20Officials%20Over%20Police%20Custody%20of%20a%20Businessman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20January%2011%2C%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Gujarat%20government%E2%80%99s%20additional%20chief%20secretary%20(home)%2C%20police%20officials%2C%20and%20an%20additional%20chief%20magistrate%20over%20sending%20a%20businessman%20to%20police%20custody%20despite%20the%20apex%20court%20granting%20him%20anticipatory%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20gross%20contempt%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20on%20the%20face%20of%20the%20record.%20How%20could%20he%20have%20been%20taken%20into%20custody%3F%20How%20could%20the%20investigating%20officer%20(IO)%20dare%20to%20seek%20the%20remand%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Mehta%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsc-contempt-notice-to-io-magistrate-over-custody-of-gujarat-businessman-9104218%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20contempt%20notices%20to%20the%20authorities%20concerned.%20%E2%80%9CLet%20this%20be%20corrected%20in%20some%20manner.%20The%20IO%20(investigating%20officer)%20and%20magistrate%20must%20learn%20some%20lessons%20from%20this.%20We%20will%20issue%20the%20notice%20for%20contempt%20to%20the%20magistrate%20also.%20Is%20this%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20they%20deal%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Order%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Justice%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C%20another%20judge%20on%20the%20division%20Bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusinessman%20Tusharbhai%20Rajnikantbhai%20Shah%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Surat%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20in%20a%20cheating%20case.%20He%20was%20granted%20an%20interim%20anticipatory%20bail%20on%20December%208%2C%202023.%20According%20to%20Shah%2C%20he%20appeared%20before%20the%20police%20on%20December%2011%20to%20support%20the%20investigation%20but%20was%20arrested%20and%20released%20on%20bail%20the%20same%20day.%20The%20police%20then%20moved%20a%20remand%20application%20on%20December%2013%20before%20a%20local%20court%20resulting%20in%20his%20police%20custody%20for%20four%20days%2C%20Shah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mehta%20was%20livid%2C%20noting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20very%20filing%20of%20the%20(remand)%20application%20was%20contempt%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%E2%80%9D%20and%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20illegal%20custody%20for%20four%20days!%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Gavai%20then%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20the%20Magistrate%20and%20the%20IO%20be%20inside%20for%20four%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20juncture%2C%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20who%20appeared%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblunder%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20investigating%20officer%20and%20tendered%20an%20apology.%20When%20the%20court%20sought%20a%20CCTV%20recording%20from%20the%20police%20station%2C%20Raju%20responded%20that%20it%20was%20not%20functional.%20To%20this%2C%20Justice%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20shows%20the%20conduct.%20On%20the%20very%20same%20day%2C%20it%20is%20not%20functioning!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mehta%20chimed%20in%2C%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20expected.%20It%E2%80%99s%20intentional%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20ask%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20civil%20nature%20case%2C%20why%20remand%20is%20required%3F%20A%20murder%20weapon%20was%20to%20be%20recovered%20or%20what%3F%E2%80%9D.%20Justice%20Mehta%20specifically%20said%20the%20authorities%20must%20explain%20why%20CCTV%20was%20not%20functioning%20on%20the%20said%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20authorities%20concerned%20to%20file%20affidavits%20explaining%20their%20response%20while%20adding%20that%20it%20may%20even%20possibly%20ask%20the%20state%20police%20chief%20to%20take%20those%20charged%20with%20contempt%20of%20court%20into%20custody%20and%20to%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Surat%20police%20commissioner%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Tomar%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20would%20get%20the%20matter%20checked%20from%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20advocate%20Syed%20accused%20Surat%20Police%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Chand-in-glove%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20complainant%20of%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20plea%20before%20the%20SC%2C%20we%20have%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Surat%20police%20worked%20hand-in-glove%20with%20the%20complainant%20and%20arrested%20Shah.%20Following%20the%20police%20remand%2C%20he%20was%20again%20produced%20before%20the%20same%20judge%20%E2%80%93%206th%20Additional%20Chief%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20D.%20S.%20Thakar%20%E2%80%93%20who%20again%20denied%20our%20plea.%20We%20filed%20a%20fresh%20bail%20application%20and%20later%20Shah%20was%20release