tal%20after%20mistakenly%20eating%C2%A0colourful%20laundry%20detergent%20pods%20that%20were%20distributed%20as%20a%20campaign%20freebie%20in%20Taiwan's%20presidential%20race%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Flifestyle%2Fhealth%2Fhealth-problems%2Fthree-people-hospitalised-after-eating-laundry-pods-in-taiwan-after-election-giveaway%2Fnews-story%2F93e5ee72db60ae74a013d4465b831e74%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThree%2520people%2520have%2520reportedly%2520been%2Cthe%2520Central%2520News%2520Agency%2520reported.%5C%22%3ENews.com.au%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20The%20pods%20were%20wrapped%20in%20clear%20packaging%20with%20photos%20of%20Nationalist%20Party%20candidate%20Hou%20Yu-ih%20and%20his%20running%20mate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20packages%20appeared%20to%20contain%20two%20smaller%20transparent%20packets%20containing%20red%20and%20green%20liquids%20and%20stated%20they%20could%20wash%20up%20to%20eight%20kilograms%20of%20clothes.%20It%20also%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BVote%20for%20number%20three%20as%20president%20to%20support%20you.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20people%20mistook%20the%20pods%20as%20candies%20and%20ate%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20hospitalised%20included%20an%2080-year-old%20man%20and%20an%2086-year-old%20woman%20who%20were%20released%20after%20having%20their%20stomachs%20flushed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHung%20Jung-chang%2C%20head%20of%20Hou's%20Chuanghua%20campaign%20office%20apologised%20for%20the%20incident%2C%20saying%20the%20office%20would%20work%20on%20%26quot%3Bdisseminating%20information%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20460%2C000%20laundry%20pods%20given%20out%20by%20the%20campaign%20were%20not%20to%20be%20eaten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20house-to-house%20visits%2C%20we%20will%20not%20distribute%20this%20kind%20of%20campaign%20material.%20We%20will%20also%20stress%20to%20our%20villagers%20through%20our%20grassroots%20organizations%20that%20they%20are%20laundry%20balls%2C%20not%20candies%2C''%20Mr.%20Hung%20said%20in%20a%20video%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Ftaiwan-election-2024-laundry-detergent-freebie-b2476105.html%5C%22%3EIndependent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20campaign%20office%20staff%20would%20visit%20the%20three%20affected%20individuals%20who%20were%20hospitalised.%20Mr%20Hung%20furtherclaimed%20that%20distribution%20of%20these%20items%20had%20been%20completed%2C%20and%20they%20would%20not%20be%20produced%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESu%20Ming-yao%2C%20an%20attending%20physician%20at%20New%20Taipei%20Municipal%20Tucheng%20Hospital's%20Department%20of%20Gastroenterology%2C%20said%20laundry%20pods%20contain%20a%20surfactant%20that%20causes%20heat%20to%20be%20released%20once%20entering%20the%20stomach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENausea%2C%20vomiting%2C%20and%20diarrhoea%20are%20the%20most%20common%20effects%20of%20ingesting%20laundry%20detergent%20pods.%C2%A0Most%20laundry%20pods%20contain%20ethanol%2C%20polymers%20and%20hydrogen%20peroxide%2C%20which%20are%20extremely%20toxic.%20People%20should%20seek%20medical%20advice%20immediately%20if%20they%20ingest%20laundry%20pods%2C%20Mr%20Su%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mr.%20Hou%20is%20running%20against%20William%20Lai%20of%20the%20governing%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%20and%20Ko%20Wen-je%20of%20the%20Taiwan%20People's%20Party%20in%20Saturday's%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704970560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fiio9hpp_laundry-pod_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F3-hospitalised-in-taiwan-after-mistakenly-eating-laundry-product-given-as-election-freebie-4841926%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20packages%20appeared%20to%20contain%20two%20smaller%20transparent%20packets%20and%20stated%2