%3EThe%20complaint%20says%20that%20the%20staff%20members%20at%20the%20serviced%20apartment%20pointed%20out%20to%20Seth%20that%20taking%20a%20flight%20would%20be%20much%20cheaper%2C%20but%20she%20%26quot%3Binsisted%26quot%3B%20on%20travelling%20in%20a%20cab.%20A%20search%20on%20flight%20booking%20websites%20reveals%20that%20even%20last-minute%20tickets%20from%20Goa%20to%20Bengaluru%20are%20available%20for%20between%20Rs%202%2C600%20and%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20passenger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20also%20said%20that%20Seth%20had%20booked%20the%20room%20from%20January%206%20to%20January%2010%20-%20and%20had%20paid%20for%20it%20in%20advance%20-%20but%20checked%20out%20at%2012.30%20am%20on%20January%208.%20The%20complaint%20was%20filed%20later%20the%20same%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeth%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20the%20alleged%20murder%2C%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Mindful%20AI%20Lab%20and%20claims%20that%20she%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bartificial%20intelligence%20ethics%20expert%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20LinkedIn%20profile%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECough%20Syrup%20Request%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20out%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20in%20his%20complaint%20in%20the%20Calangute%20police%20station%2C%20Gagan%20Gambhir%2C%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20Sol%20Banyan%20Grande%20serviced%20apartment%20in%20Candolim%2C%20said%20Seth%20and%20her%20four-year-old%20son%20had%20checked%20in%20on%20the%20night%20of%20January%206%20and%20were%20staying%20in%20Room%20404.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengaluru-ceo-suchana-seth-accused-of-killing-son-asked-husband-to-meet-child-day-before-murder-4840217%5C%22%3ECEO%20Accused%20Of%20Killing%20Son%20Texted%20Husband%20The%20Day%20She%20Checked%20Into%20Goa%20Hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gambhir%20states%20that%2C%20around%204%20pm%20the%20next%20day%2C%20Seth%20made%