2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20significantly%20scale%20up%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shouvik%20Dhar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESpreading%20the%20joy%20of%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Silchar%2C%20Assam%2C%20Shouvik%20developed%20a%20fondness%20for%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20While%20pursuing%20his%20studies%20at%20NIT%20Silchar%2C%20Shouvik%20had%20no%20initial%20plans%20of%20venturing%20into%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20my%20engineering%2C%20I%20joined%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335025%2Fclean-drinking-water-from-thin-air-scientists-breakthrough-revolutionises-access-to-pure-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20DRDO%20as%20a%20scientist%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Though%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20envisioned%20a%20career%20switch%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20strong%20inclination%20to%20pursue%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20stint%20with%20DRDO%2C%20Shouvik%20decided%20to%20pursue%20an%20MBA.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20my%20MBA%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20starting%20my%20own%20venture%20was%20my%20true%20calling.%20Before%20Zomoz%2C%20I%20ventured%20into%20several%20businesses%2C%20ranging%20from%20a%20skill%20training%20company%20to%20a%20tech%20firm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmomos-3-1704806867.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shouvik%20realised%20that%20there%20were%20no%20good%20momo%20places%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20decided%20to%20start%20Zomoz.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2