99%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAman%20says%20he%20has%20always%20focussed%20on%20selling%20jackfruit%20to%20uplift%20its%20social%20status.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9DAt%20a%20time%20when%20people%20were%20focused%20on%20producing%20protein-based%20foods%20in%20labs%2C%20the%20nutrient-rich%20jackfruit%20was%20going%20to%20waste.%20I%20planned%20to%20work%20towards%20a%20better%20value%20proposition%20of%20this%20fruit%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20founder%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%20to%20yours%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Kathalfy%20has%20been%20able%20to%20stack%20thousands%20of%20household%20pantries%20with%20jackfruit%20food%20items.%20Every%20month%2C%20the%20brand%20caters%20to%20at%20least%20600%20orders%20from%20across%20the%20country%20majorly%20from%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20journey%20also%20came%20with%20its%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20the%20first%20being%20conceptualising%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20unique%20food%20items.%20During%20the%20initial%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Aman%20met%20several%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F186190%2Fkarnataka-family-rare-jackfruit-earns-lakhs-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejackfruit%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20food%20scientists%2C%20and%20institutions%20to%20come%20up%20with%20unique%20recipes.%20But%20no%20one%20could%20satisfactorily%20help%20him%20in%20developing%20the%20products%20he%20envisioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA5J1M4gmSKM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with