n%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20after%20three%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Kathalfy%20was%20able%20to%20launch%20the%20products%20in%20April%20last%20year%2C%20though%20being%20formally%20registered%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20Indians%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20food%2C%20taste%20is%20the%20most%20important%20factor.%20Hence%20developing%20products%20that%20are%20delectable%20to%20the%20taste%20buds%20while%20retaining%20their%20nutrients%20and%20keeping%20them%20free%20of%20artificial%20chemicals%20has%20always%20been%20my%20goal.%20I%20only%20wanted%20to%20sell%20products%20that%20my%20family%20and%20I%20would%20consume%20ourselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20day%20one%2C%20I%20have%20focussed%20on%20selling%20jackfruit%20to%20uplift%20its%20social%20status.%20Unlike%20other%20brands%2C%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20term%20it%20a%20meat%20replacement%20product.%20Instead%2C%20I%20always%20promote%20jackfruit%20for%20what%20it%20is%2C%20which%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20our%20brand%20name%20Kathalfy%2C%20which%20is%20%3Cem%3EKathal%3C%2Fem%3E%20plus%20Simplify.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20glad%20that%20our%20customer%20base%20is%20increasing%20month%20on%20month%20and%20people%20once%20again%20are%20including%20%3Cem%3Ekathal%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20their%20diets%20while%20loving%20the%20taste%20of%20our%20products.%20Anyway%2C%20it%20is%20just%20the%20beginning.%20There%20is%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20buy%20jackfruit-based%20products%20from%20Kathalfy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathalfy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Kathalfy%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fh5%